
in_ten_sity

intensity = 強度 / 劇烈程度 / 力量大小

1. 當作主詞 (Subject)
放在句首，作為整個句子討論的核心。

公式： The intensity of + 名詞 + 動詞...
範例：
The intensity of the light is too high. (光線的強度太高了。)
The intensity of the competition increased. (競爭的激烈程度增加了。)

2. 當作受詞 (Object)
放在及物動詞或介係詞之後，作為動作的接受者。

公式： 動詞 + intensity 或 介係詞 + intensity

範例：
動詞後： We need to reduce the intensity of the workout. (我們需要減低運動的強度。)
介係詞後： He spoke with great intensity. (他說話時語氣非常強烈。)




The intensity of the light is too high.
The intensity of the database migration is increasing.
The intensity of Kipper's barking is loud.


The intensity of the sun is very high today.
She runs with great intensity.
The teacher spoke with intensity.
Exercise increases the intensity of your heartbeat.
The storm reached its full intensity at night.


⚠️ 小提醒
intensity = 名詞
intense = 形容詞（強烈的）
intensely = 副詞（強烈地 / 專注地）
